  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要做一个用户下单的用户旅程图，核心目标是展示从购物车到最终确认订单的完整流程。我建议分成两大阶段：先处理购物车，再填写订单信息。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Making an order",
        "Inspect shopping cart",
        "Provide information"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，标题定为\"Making an order\"。第一个section叫\"Inspect shopping cart\"对吗？里面需要包含哪些具体步骤？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "title",
        "Inspect shopping cart"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "购物车环节有四个关键动作：进入购物车、修改数量、删除商品，然后继续去结算。用户评分的话，进购物车和去结算都是4分，改数量3分，删除商品只有2分——因为删东西体验不太好。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Go to shopping cart",
        "Change quantity",
        "Remove item",
        "Proceed to checkout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，第一部分已添加：Go to shopping cart (4分)、Change quantity (3分)、Remove item (2分)、Proceed to checkout (4分)。现在处理第二个section\"Provide information\"，请描述具体步骤。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Inspect shopping cart",
        "Proceed to checkout"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "信息填写部分也是四步：选择收货地址、选择配送方式、选择支付方式，最后确认订单。地址选择和最终确认都是4分，配送和支付方式选择是3分。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Choose delivery address",
        "Select shipping method",
        "Select payment method",
        "Confirm order"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认一下：Choose delivery address (4分)、Select shipping method (3分)、Select payment method (3分)、Confirm order (4分)。所有actor都是User对吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Choose delivery address",
        "Select shipping method",
        "Select payment method",
        "Confirm order"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，全是User。这个旅程图完整覆盖了从查看购物车到最终确认订单的全过程，两个section的划分也符合实际业务流程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "User",
        "Inspect shopping cart",
        "Provide information"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已完成。整个journey包含两个section共8个步骤，评分从2到4分分布，清晰展现了用户下单的情感曲线——购物车环节删除商品体验最低，结算和信息确认环节体验较好。",
      "elements_involved": [
